    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/6ec3afa6cfe182cd9ea7dcda59d836a7.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=72 /></span>看似平和的满月野镇，背后却充斥各种不稳定因素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种被称为梦魇的怪物撕裂了异世与现界的分界线，开始进入现实世界危害民众。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自月见里研究所的凛堂八叶和她的伙伴们一起挺身而出，决定对抗这些异常事物，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >封印不同的异界，并拯救整座城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/f2595b679c34da789a546ced0b019160.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在经典回合制游戏当中与梦魇相抗衡吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在异界中探索的队员们，个个身怀绝技并且专精于不同的技能，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是肉搏专家，剑术大师还是神社的巫女，总有一名队员能够对应您眼前的状况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此之外，您还可以通过拥有各类神秘的守护灵来强化她们的力量，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使她们在战斗的过程中更加得心应手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了可以强化队伍中的成员们的力量以外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护灵还可以让队员们获得全新的技能，被动能力，以及各种元素抗性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过您并不需要时刻关注守护灵的装备情况，也不用频繁更换队员们已经装备的守护灵，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为每名队员都只能装备特定种类的守护灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此您只需要收集这些守护灵，就能稳定提升队伍的战斗力，而并不需要经常对装备的状况做出改变！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在紧张刺激的战斗之余，您也可以在满月野镇中进行探索！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是八叶的故乡，也是一个超自然现象与民间传说层出不穷的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在城市里自由探索时，您有机会获得强大的装备与道具，也有可能遇到心怀不轨的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八月和她的伙伴们究竟要如何应对种种挑战，实现她们的目标呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/2a9fe0e5f5b784953f2bd3857dc1f680.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/14850e33c733fd2f19457f8b125a6c91.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/084bdb6483512bfdbf5b2fa1b69b77de.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/7026e5189c3e2bb7b585abeb98d31489.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551560/extras/cc62af148e446af0de1d6a19de44fbef.avif?t=1749282339\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>立足于现代世界的奇幻冒险</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然这部游戏的舞台被设定在了现代日本，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但您也可以通过现实与异界之间的裂隙进入扭曲的梦境世界中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从不同的角度在似曾相识的地点冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可供个性化设定的角色们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过更换角色们持有的守护灵来让这些角色们获得独特的能力，在战斗中大放异彩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对敌人的弱点重拳出击！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种敌人都会使用某种属性的攻击，也都具有对于某种属性的弱点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用属性的相生相克来对敌人造成大量伤害，并且强化我方角色们的防御吧！</p>",
